text: Veronica Cojuhari (born 3 October 1998) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a midfielder and a forward for Women's Championship club Anenii Noi and the Moldova women's national team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Moldovan women's footballers Category:Moldova women's international footballers
